      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It will require substantial mechanical attention and cosmetic restoration to return to reliable service. The engine runs roughly and likely needs a major overhaul, while the transmission exhibits significant slipping during gear changes. Externally, there is visible rust, multiple dents, and the paint is heavily faded; the interior shows heavy wear including torn upholstery and several non-functional electronic components. This car is an ideal candidate for a dedicated project or as a source for parts.",
