    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This distinguished vehicle represents a superb opportunity for the discerning driver. Meticulously maintained and subjected to a rigorous multi-point inspection by our certified technicians, it offers robust performance paired with a refined aesthetic. Every aspect of this automobile reflects a commitment to quality and mechanical excellence, ensuring a driving experience that is both reliable and sophisticated. We invite you to experience the superior handling and preserved elegance of this exceptional model.",
      "price": 38500.0,
