      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example utilizes a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to send power through a factory M Variable Differential Lock. Technical highlights include a recently performed valve shim adjustment and a comprehensive inspection of the rear subframe reinforcement points. The chassis dynamics are preserved through refreshed bushings and a well-sorted suspension geometry, maintaining the platform's signature 50/50 weight distribution and tactile steering feedback. While showing minor signs of road use, the powertrain remains in peak operating condition, delivering a linear power band up to the 8,000 RPM redline.",
      "price": 34500.0,
